{"tid":26522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港鐵北角站招牌涉僭建　屋署下令60日內拆除","createTime":"2016-12-06T18:19:57.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T02:24:21.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e1c7ada43534fdffd22d1f524986d8c74d4561f","tid":26522,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"屋宇署在港鐵北角站張貼告示，指該站位於七姊妹道的出入口有一個懸掛式招牌和支架屬於僭建，下令港鐵在60日內完成拆除工程。港鐵回應本網查詢時，指已經知悉事件並會作出跟進。 <br />\n<br />\n　　屋宇署昨日發出告示，指有關招牌的建築工程未有根據《建築物條例》經建築事務監督批准圖則，以及取得同意。按照條例，署方要求港鐵進行拆卸工程，並需於30日內展開，60日內完成。 <br />\n<br />\n　　港鐵回應時證實事件，指公司一直致力為乘客提供安全及舒適乘車環境，已知悉有關部門就北角站B4出入口外一個車站招牌的通知，會作出適切跟進。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%99%E6%8B%9B%E7%89%8C%E6%B6%89%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA-%E5%B1%8B%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A460%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4-133300703.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2590%25B5%25E5%258C%2597%25E8%25A7%2592%25E7%25AB%2599%25E6%258B%259B%25E7%2589%258C%25E6%25B6%2589%25E5%2583%25AD%25E5%25BB%25BA-%25E5%25B1%258B%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E4%25B8%258B%25E4%25BB%25A460%25E6%2597%25A5%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%258B%2586%25E9%2599%25A4-133300703.html&d=SKgAetXxONuB2%2Fe424LtrXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=64b69029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B8%AF%E9%90%B5%E5%8C%97%E8%A7%92%E7%AB%99%E6%8B%9B%E7%89%8C%E6%B6%89%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA-%E5%B1%8B%E7%BD%B2%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%A460%E6%97%A5%E5%85%A7%E6%8B%86%E9%99%A4-133300703.html</a>"},{"pid":"443e999748ce5fbe776ac04135e340c90f5bd74e","tid":26522,"uid":2739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-06T20:07:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/07/040724_e4a974dc1ac6050992ddb0224038be1f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F07%2F040724_e4a974dc1ac6050992ddb0224038be1f.jpg&h=794694ea&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5